_:Nd665e840409042d9b762eb4c6caa8760 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Anna Turley was appointed Minister of State in the Cabinet Office (Minister without Portfolio) on 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was previously Junior Lord of the Treasury (Government Whip) from 10 July 2024 to 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the MP for Redcar in July 2024.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
